app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: This is a 5/5 app! Even tho some of the skin wouldn't work/bug/T pose. Please update more upcoming skins this 2025!
reviews.replyContent: Thank you for the 5-star review! We’re always working to improve the app and add more skins. Could you let us know which skin is bugged or in a T-pose? Please email us with the details so we can fix it: injector.origin@gmail.com.

reviews.content: It works, half of it does. Some effect won't appear or either corrupted the effects are there but the hero looks the same, odd. And I appreciate the consistent updates despite mlbb is updating frequently and it needs to catch up.
